⚡️Why Use Helm Charts?

✅️Simplifies Kubernetes application deployment and management.
✅️Allows parameterization via values.yaml for flexible configurations.
✅️Enables version control and rollback of deployments.

✅️Chart.yaml → Defines metadata like name, version, and description.

✅️values.yaml → Stores default configuration values (can override).

✅️templates/ → Contains Kubernetes YAML templates (e.g deployment, service)
